---
title: Sequence Diagram - Manajemen Kamar (CRUD)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Mgr as Manager
    participant UI as Halaman /rooms
    participant API as /api/rooms
    participant DB as Supabase

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    note right of Mgr: CREATE Kamar Baru
    Mgr->>UI: Klik "Tambah Kamar"
    UI->>API: POST { number, type, base_price, status }
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO rooms (...)
    DB-->>API: { id, ... }
    API-->>UI: 201 Created
    UI-->>Mgr: Tampilkan kamar baru di tabel
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
    note right of Mgr: READ Daftar Kamar
    Mgr->>UI: Load /rooms
    UI->>API: GET /api/rooms?status=...
    API->>DB: SELECT * FROM rooms ORDER BY number
    DB-->>API: rooms[]
    API-->>UI: 200 OK
    UI-->>Mgr: Tabel kamar dengan badge status
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
    note right of Mgr: UPDATE Status Kamar
    Mgr->>UI: Ubah status (available → cleaning)
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/rooms/:id { status }
    API->>DB: UPDATE rooms SET status=? WHERE id=?
    DB-->>API: ok
    API-->>UI: 200
    UI-->>Mgr: Badge update real-time
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 238)
    note right of Mgr: DELETE Kamar
    Mgr->>UI: Klik hapus + konfirmasi
    UI->>API: DELETE /api/rooms/:id
    API->>DB: Cek reservasi aktif
    alt Ada reservasi aktif
        API-->>UI: 409 Conflict
        UI-->>Mgr: Tidak dapat dihapus
    else Aman
        API->>DB: DELETE FROM rooms WHERE id=?
        DB-->>API: ok
        API-->>UI: 204
    end
    end
